# Metronia Water Services MQTT ACL
# Least-privilege access by device role and topic.

user sensor01
topic write mws/water/plant1/tankA/quality/telemetry
topic write mws/water/plant1/tankA/quality/alerts

user operator01
topic read mws/water/plant1/tankA/quality/#

user ids01
topic read mws/#
topic read $SYS/#

# Lab-only test identity. It may connect/read a non-operational public area only.
# It cannot publish false telemetry to the operational topic.
user attacker01
topic read mws/public/#
